flowRoot.flowPara: class Point with x, y; def Point.init(x, y) { this.x = x; this.y = y; } def Point.toString() { return "Point(" + this.x + ", " + this.y + ")"; } class ThreeDeePoint extends Point with z; def ThreeDeePoint.init(x, y, z) { super.init(x, y); this.z = z; } def ThreeDeePoint.toString() { return "ThreeDeePoint(" + this.x + ", " + this.y + ", " + this.z + ")";}
class ThreeDeePoint extends Point with z;
